'''''Nous aurons toute la mort pour dormir''''' , ni 1977 filime ya documentaire ya [[Ubufaransa|Franco]] - [[Moritaniya|Mauritanian]] iyobowe na Med Hondo kandi ikorerwa muri Les Films du Soleil Ô.  

Iyi filime yafashwe amezi 4 kuva ku ya 25 Ukuboza 1975 kugeza ku ya 5 Werurwe 1976, mu gace kahoze ari Sahara ya [[Esipanye]].  Iyi filime ivuga ku ntambara yitwaje intwaro ya Polisario Front mu burengerazuba bwa Sahara kurwanya ubukoloni bwa Espagne.  Iyi filime yakiriwe neza n'abayinenga kandi yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Berlin mu [[Budage]] bw'Iburengerazuba muri Kamena 1977.  

 
